The paper is about machine reading comprehension, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP) and artificial intelligence (AI). The paper proposes a new model for MRC tasks, which involves both reading and verification strategies. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which covers NLP and related topics. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), which are all relevant to the topic of MRC and the proposed model.
